603
00:34:34,220 --> 00:34:35,570
I don't blame you.

604
00:34:36,090 --> 00:34:37,330
I'm just a little disappointed.

605
00:34:37,730 --> 00:34:38,820
Your uncle

606
00:34:39,300 --> 00:34:40,900
