to the Deer Hunt now.

612
00:35:04,010 --> 00:35:05,530
You're put in a tough spot.

613
00:35:06,530 --> 00:35:07,460
I can understand.

614
00:35:19,780 --> 00:35:20,980
Can't you just be

615
00:35:22,740 --> 00:35:23,940
my wife?

616
00:35:34,740 --> 00:35:36,860
(Chijun, Liangya)

617
00:35:36,860 --> 00:35:39,340
(Mansion of the Lord of Liangya,
Liangya)

618
00:36:05,380 --> 00:36:07,260
I've already told you.

619
00:36:07,780 --> 00:36:09,170
The Lady

620
00:36:09,690 --> 00:36:11,610
is being favored now,

621
00:36:11,860 --> 00:36:13,900
so we can't confront her head-on.

622
00:36:15,210 --> 00:36:17,300
You always say
we should keep a low profile,

623
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:19,730
