that might cause future trouble.

624
00:36:20,380 --> 00:36:22,340
She whispers in Father's ear every day,

625
00:36:22,780 --> 00:36:24,740
wanting her son Liu Qi
to become the heir.

626
00:36:25,210 --> 00:36:27,170
Do you think
practicing martial arts here

627
00:36:27,170 --> 00:36:28,860
will solve everything?

628
00:36:29,530 --> 00:36:32,260
You need to spend more time
pleasing the Lord.

629
00:36:32,780 --> 00:36:35,010
As long as you win his favor,

630
00:36:35,460 --> 00:36:36,820
she can provoke all she wants,

631
00:36:36,980 --> 00:36:38,130
but it won't matter.

632
00:36:38,980 --> 00:36:39,820
Remember:

633
00:36:40,010 --> 00:36:41,260
At the end of the day,

634
00:36:41,340 --> 00:36:42,820
you are the rightful heir.

635
00:36:44,340 --> 00:36:45,210
Got it?

636
00:37:04,820 --> 00:37:05,980
I heard

637
00:37:06,420 --> 00:37:08,650
that Wei is about to hold the Deer Hunt.

638
00:37:09,010 --> 00:37:09,940
The invitation

639
00:37:09,940 --> 00:37:11,980
has been delivered to the Lord.

640
00:37:12,740 --> 00:37:15,570
I believe that if you seize this chance

641
00:37:15,570 --> 00:37:17,170
and make a name for yourself,

642
00:37:17,690 --> 00:37:18,980
your position as the heir

643
00:37:19,380 --> 00:37:21,380
will be secure.

644
00:37:24,210 --> 00:37:25,610
If I go to Wei,

645
00:37:26,170 --> 00:37:28,530
I'm afraid she'll have her way
by father's side.

646
00:37:32,820 --> 00:37:33,860
You have

647
00:37:33,980 --> 00:37:35,530
always been

648
00:37:35,530 --> 00:37:37,010
so indecisive.

649
00:37:39,610 --> 00:37:41,090
I must remind you.

650
00:37:41,380 --> 00:37:42,860
Your position right now

651
00:37:42,860 --> 00:37:44,860
is precarious.

652
00:37:51,650 --> 00:37:52,490
Young Master,

653
00:37:55,780 --> 00:37:57,130
the Lord has sent someone

654
00:37:57,130 --> 00:37:57,970
to call for you.

655
00:38:04,740 --> 00:38:05,580
Father.

656
00:38:06,780 --> 00:38:07,620
My Lady.

657
00:38:13,170 --> 00:38:14,650
The reason I called you here today

658
00:38:15,130 --> 00:38:17,170
is regarding the Deer Hunt.

659
00:38:18,300 --> 00:38:21,380
I've decided to take Qi to Yujun.

660
00:38:29,340 --> 00:38:30,650
Qi is not yet eight years old.

661
00:38:31,010 --> 00:38:31,860
I'm afraid

662
00:38:32,090 --> 00:38:33,820
people will laugh at us

663
00:38:34,090 --> 00:38:35,330
for having a child represent us.

664
00:38:35,940 --> 00:38:37,130
Father, please reconsider.

665
00:38:37,740 --> 00:38:39,300
The invitation says

666
00:38:39,460 --> 00:38:41,260
