to attend.

667
00:38:42,210 --> 00:38:43,420
With the Lord there,

668
00:38:43,780 --> 00:38:45,650
who'd bully Qi for being young?

669
00:38:46,460 --> 00:38:48,170
If there's anything to laugh about,

670
00:38:48,490 --> 00:38:50,860
you lost your engagement

671
00:38:51,050 --> 00:38:53,050
and Panyi to the Lord of Wei

672
00:38:53,340 --> 00:38:55,090
and even offended him.

673
00:38:55,690 --> 00:38:57,980
If it weren't
for your repeated mistakes,

674
00:38:58,010 --> 00:39:00,090
why would your father
have to travel at his age

675
00:39:00,090 --> 00:39:01,480
to reconcile with the Lord of Wei?

676
00:39:02,530 --> 00:39:04,420
