680
00:39:11,820 --> 00:39:12,860
My Lord...

681
00:39:12,860 --> 00:39:13,760
How impudent!

682
00:39:13,860 --> 00:39:15,530
How dare you defy your mother?

683
00:39:18,010 --> 00:39:19,820
My mother passed away long ago.

684
00:39:20,090 --> 00:39:21,210
My Lord,

685
00:39:21,490 --> 00:39:23,820
Maoqing has never accepted me
as his stepmother

686
00:39:23,940 --> 00:39:25,530
and has insulted me repeatedly.

687
00:39:26,740 --> 00:39:28,610
You wicked woman, shut up.

688
00:39:36,610 --> 00:39:38,010
If you defy us again,

689
00:39:38,010 --> 00:39:39,400
I'll deprive you of your position.

690
00:39:40,340 --> 00:39:41,490
Leave at once!

691
00:39:48,010 --> 00:39:48,980
Father,

692
00:39:51,050 --> 00:39:52,610
