693
00:39:55,740 --> 00:39:56,690
Guards!

694
00:39:56,780 --> 00:39:57,690
Guards!

695
00:40:08,300 --> 00:40:09,340
Please spare me!

696
00:40:34,170 --> 00:40:35,090
Why?

697
00:40:36,130 --> 00:40:38,050
Why must you commit parricide?

698
00:40:40,940 --> 00:40:43,090
You always think I'm indecisive, right?

699
00:40:44,010 --> 00:40:44,850
What's wrong?

700
00:40:45,940 --> 00:40:47,690
Now, I've become the Lord of Liangya.

701
00:40:48,420 --> 00:40:49,900
Aren't you happy about it?

702
00:40:50,050 --> 00:40:52,260
You are the legitimate heir.

703
00:40:52,610 --> 00:40:56,050
